nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If I had opened 4@H, which is possible, then it should go P-P and East should reopen with a double and West should pass. West should not double a 4@H opener. That is not penalty per se. It is just cards, and does not promise heart tricks. |
