cp|8|AT|^^
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|A 4NT bid over 4@H shows the minors. Interestingly, if an opponent opens 4@S and you bid 4NT, that shows any 2 suits. Perhaps the minors or perhaps hearts and a minor. |
