nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So responder to the 4NT bid over 4@S can't bid 5@D unless they are willing to play 5@H. Partner bids 5@C if willing to play 5C or 5@D or partner bids 5@C if willing to play 5@C or 5 in either red suit.|
