nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So if partner bids 5@C and the 4NT bidder has diamonds and hearts they pull 5@C to 5@D and the 5@C bidder either passes or corrects to 5@H. If partner bids 5@D over 4NT, then partner is saying they are willing to play in either 5@D or 5@H.|
